channel.title: Tides of war!
channel.description:
hey i made a server its pretty cool (i guess)
its got working cassles wars (except one of the staires dont work)
It has to seperate teams (Dark brotherhood, and the Assassins)
each team has its own town
it has a thing that makes you transform into a barrows ghost if you have full barrows on its wild is dependent on you, if you want to be in wild you can click the button that makes whole world wild, if you dont then the whole world is non wild.
its a pretty cool server i guess, i have to give some creds to Red scape... =D
heres the link http://uppit.com/G77L1M
